      "value": "<p>Some embri’s flesh grows up and around their masks. For such embri, being unmasked exposes raw nerves and inflicts constant painful distraction. While such an embri has its mask removed, it has a –2 penalty to ability checks and skill checks and must roll all Reflex saving throws twice and take the lower result.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces masked emotions.</strong></p>\n<p><em></em></p><em></em><p><em>Equip mask Item to reverse penalties: @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.KaqNfSwwuzofl4PN]{Embri Mask (Fleshbound Mask)}</em></p>"
